This software includes adaptations of code from the following open-source projects:

- SpikF (WWJ-creator/SpikF) — adapted for integration into the unified framework
- SeqSNN (microsoft/SeqSNN, MIT License) — Spikformer, Spikingformer, QKFormer, iSpikformer, SpikeRNN, SpikTCN, SpikGRU
- TS-LIF (kkking-kk/TS-LIF) — TSFormer, TSGRU, TSTCN (two-compartment LIF neurons)
- Time-Series-Library (thuml/Time-Series-Library, MIT License) — DLinear and framework conventions
- iTransformer (thuml/iTransformer, MIT License) — iTransformer ANN baseline

